Texts.Chs: 一个名为泽尔迪亚的人的全身肖像。
Texts.Eng: A full-body portrait of someone named Zeldia.

Texts.Chs: 喂，为什么一个人类居然长有翅膀，而我却没有？
Texts.Eng: Hey, why does a human get to have wings when I don't?

Texts.Chs: 屠杀者才才才会有翅膀。不知知道他的味道好不好。
Texts.Eng: Meatman hass wingss. Unssure if would tasste good.

Texts.Chs: 让我回想起了一款非常古老的街机游戏——当地球还存在的时候。
Texts.Eng: Reminds me of a very old arcade game I once played when Earth was still around.

Texts.Chs: 看，这里有一位非常漂亮的女士！
Texts.Eng: That there's one mighty fine looking lady!

Texts.Chs: 这里所描绘的女人看起来像是把人类和翼族人混合起来所得到的一样。
Texts.Eng: The woman depicted here looks like what you'd get if you mashed a human and an avian together.

Texts.Chs: 这让我想起了我的同学们在无聊时会画的人类艺术，那可真下流。
Texts.Eng: This reminds me of risque art my classmates would draw of humans when really bored.

Texts.Chs: 不管她是谁，她看起来就像科技发展部试图创造的那种人一样。
Texts.Eng: Whoever this is, she looks like someone the Miniknog would have attempted to create.
